<item>
            <title>[LU-1604] md_ucred() shouldn&apos;t be called in osd-ldiskfs when running with OFD</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1604</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;md_ucred() is called in several places (in osd_push_ctxt() used by quota, but also in __osd_oi_insert()) in osd-ldiskfs. This code ends up calling a function in mdd and should thus not be executed when using OFD.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="15141">LU-1604</key>
            <summary>md_ucred() shouldn&apos;t be called in osd-ldiskfs when running with OFD</summary>
